# Freelio

**Live Site: https://freelio-new.netlify.app/

## Project Overview
Freelio is a freelance marketplace platform where users can post jobs, accept tasks, and manage their accepted jobs. It provides a simple and intuitive interface for freelancers and clients to collaborate effectively.

## Features
-Post New Jobs: Users can create and post jobs with a title, category, summary, and cover image.
-Browse Latest Jobs:** Display the newest freelance jobs in a clean, grid-based layout.
-Accept Jobs:** Freelancers can accept jobs and view them in their personal “Accepted Tasks” page.
-Manage Accepted Tasks:** Users can mark tasks as DONE or CANCEL, instantly updating the UI and database.
-Authentication Integration:** Secure user login with Firebase authentication and personalized dashboards.